'''VibroSword Squadron''' was a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Squadron/Legends|squadron]] that was composed of [[Eta-5 interceptor]]s. [[Syal Antilles]], under the alias of Lysa Dunter, was part of the squadron, and was known as "V-Sword Seven." A [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]], serving as V-Sword Ten, flew as her [[Wingmate/Legends|wingmate]]. The unit participated in [[Operation Roundabout]] and was stationed aboard the battle carrier [[Dodonna (Galactic-class)|''Dodonna'']].

